### NotificationService API Testing
### This file contains HTTP requests that can be used to test the NotificationService API

@NotificationService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5236
@jwt_token = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check
GET {{NotificationService_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

